16.12.2007:
 - Default inittab now copied from 'system' to overlay (if none in
   overlay.xpk), removed from live_files.

2007.12.09
 - Version 5.0.5
 - Added acceptance of 'root=' boot option to select location of larch system.
   In this case the root directory must contain a file 'larchroot' (not
   'larchboot'!).
